{"tid":1932572,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"（求救）今年考DSE 近排經常失眠","createTime":"2020-03-18T20:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T20:49:55.000Z","uid":249971,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"4752a93828e002d61d281563f53a830ed6d353fc","tid":1932572,"uid":249971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T20:50:07.000Z","msg":"DSE就快到<br />\n唔知點解最近不停失眠<br />\n呢兩個禮拜有四日失眠<br />\n一開始係轆到四五點先訓到<br />\n第二次啪咗粒必理痛先訓到<br />\n第三次啪咗都訓唔到<br />\n最近兩次係成晚訓唔到<br />\n尋晚買咗pukka甜睡茶飲 但都請問係訓唔到<br />\n我可以點做先訓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就嚟DSE我真係要崩潰啦"},{"pid":"7c9c99ba4a16d9ff4588b84155847250448fb025","tid":1932572,"uid":152222,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T20:51:44.000Z","msg":"訓唔着咪繼續温書lo"},{"pid":"c62626ed049233aac80ca868fba715253b5c0491","tid":1932572,"uid":152222,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T20:53:45.000Z","msg":"你越緊張越崩潰就越難訓得着"},{"pid":"e9b0b39d30e0aefa76b152ebb1dc470207614034","tid":1932572,"uid":249971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7c9c99ba4a16d9ff4588b84155847250448fb025","tid":1932572,"uid":152222,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T20:51:44.000Z","msg":"訓唔着咪繼續温書lo"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T20:53:59.000Z","msg":"但係咁咪休息唔夠冇精神？"},{"pid":"9083ca0eeea6dd73321d8fa6cf5112d79e4b2012","tid":1932572,"uid":249971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c62626ed049233aac80ca868fba715253b5c0491","tid":1932572,"uid":152222,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T20:53:45.000Z","msg":"你越緊張越崩潰就越難訓得着"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T20:54:33.000Z","msg":"點先唔緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba016d796f421753856492bb0bfb89550700edd5","tid":1932572,"uid":15739,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T20:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgm