a9a25","tid":1932572,"uid":314679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T20:58:34.000Z","msg":"加<br />\n油<br />\n！<br />\n<br />\n唔好咁緊張 有時間不如溫多陣書"},{"pid":"11f328fafbff9c3531b03e0551e58653cc924229","tid":1932572,"uid":142378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T20:59:11.000Z","msg":"當年我溫書成日溫溫吓瞓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主瞓唔著嘅試吓做啲無聊嘢放鬆吓心情 太緊張都會影響溫書效率"},{"pid":"02869839b17707a02c07765b2bdff9fc41c3dfe5","tid":1932572,"uid":302895,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T20:59:26.000Z","msg":"考前一日訓唔到 四點先訓 一黎就考最廢既中文reading 結果二左<br />\n諗住短板 但之後慢慢習慣左就好了<br />\n<br />\n樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真心話黎既<br />\ndse只要開始左第一科 你就會開始豁達的了 就唔會再咁緊張嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n而家未殺到埋身 訓到就訓 訓唔到就做啲你想做既野啦<br />\n喺床上碌黎碌去都於事無補嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 千祈唔好食藥 會依賴的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4c7a99a2dbed8ed4eadc72f173bfc65f3cbd24","tid":1932572,"uid":152222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9083ca0eeea6dd73321d8fa6cf5112d79e4b2012","tid":1932572,"uid":249971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c62626ed049233aac80ca868fba715253b5c0491","tid":1932572,"uid":152222,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T20:53:45.000Z","msg":"你越緊張越崩潰就越難訓得着"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T20:54:33.000Z","msg":"點先唔緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T21:01:42.000Z","msg":"放鬆D深呼吸先，然後訓落張床到，訓住咁玩手機之類，總之就係要令自己放鬆，唔再諗考試温書D野，然後自然會想訓教"},{"pid":"06c46f1f86d5e422668cfde1456fcb51b6b0d68f","tid":1932572,"uid":96098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9083ca0eeea6dd73321d8fa6cf5112d79e4b2012","tid":1932572,"uid":249971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c62626ed049233aac80ca868fba715253b5c0491","tid":1932572,"uid":152222,"like":6,"