faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T21:11:17.000Z","msg":"而且你真係要諗方法令自己隨時都可以放鬆同冷靜到，因為你遲D真係考嘅時候可能更加緊張，可能會令你考得更差（因人而異，可能有D人越緊張考得越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，由其是說話同聆聽，所以你應該要諗方法令自己可以隨時都冷靜放鬆到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95e6e54609e01272b961acc38187c871858e049","tid":1932572,"uid":249971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba016d796f421753856492bb0bfb89550700edd5","tid":1932572,"uid":15739,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T20:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T21:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89dd0767f503bc3b75095f241b4c048b9a8f3660","tid":1932572,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T21:12:29.000Z","msg":"加油 我係你對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391effcc88fa71ceafa9f0b78d7b217f6eb77f97","tid":1932572,"uid":280056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T21:13:05.000Z","msg":"回想下自己中學邊堂成日訓 （其實你想嘅話全科都得）<br />\n攤係床個陣係自己腦海溫書<br />\n唔洗背出黎 諗就得<br />\n每一課背曬啲keypoint出黎<br />\n諗下一啲facts咁<br />\n溫溫下就會訓到 自己都唔知自己訓左"},{"pid":"91f8d418f33f810736bb58c910b4bc185626e16e","tid":1932572,"uid":249971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02869839b17707a02c07765b2bdff9fc41c3dfe5","tid":1932572,"uid":302895,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T20:59:26.000Z","msg":"考前一日訓唔到 四點先訓 一黎就考最廢既中文reading 結果二左<br />\n諗住短板 但之後慢慢習慣左就好了<br />\n<br />\n樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真心話黎既<br />\ndse只要開始左第一科 你就會開始豁達的了 就唔會再咁緊張嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n而家未殺到埋身 訓到就訓 訓唔到就做啲你想做既野啦<br />\n喺床上碌黎碌去都於事無補嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" cl